<li>Schiller, Paul, <i>Rudolf Steiner and Initiation</i>. Steiner Books, 1990.</li>
<li>Swassjan, Karen, <i>The Ultimate Communion of Mankind: A Celebration of Rudolf Steiner's Book "The Philosophy of Freedom"</i>, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0904693821" class="internal">ISBN 0-904693-82-1</a></li>
