<li>Turgeniev, Assya, <i>Reminiscences of Rudolf Steiner and Work on the First Goetheanum</i>, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1902636406" class="internal">ISBN 1-902636-40-6</a></li>
<li>Welburn, Andrew, <i>Rudolf Steiner's Philosophy and the Crisis of Contemporary Thought</i>, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0863154360" class="internal">ISBN 0-86315-436-0</a></li>
<li>Wilkinson, Roy, <i>Rudolf Steiner: An Introduction to his Spiritual World-View</i>, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1902636287" class="internal">ISBN 1902636287</a></li>
